          "reviewBody": "Wish I could give them 0 star. This school literally tried to spoil my future and i still remember how principal and teachers were against creative students and creativity talents. I use to take art classes from outside because they don’t offer art classes in 11-12th. No value to art and craft. They even take extra cuticular period to Maths.\nDuring my 12th 2018, i was supposed to give my NIFT entrance exam somewhere in December.\nMy leave wasn’t signed by principal, i still took leave and went for it. Next day they charged my 2000 per day leave. Bcz I WENT TO GIVE MY ENTRANCE EXAM.\nLet me tell this school.. my result came of NIFT delhi. I scored AIR 7th 2017.\nI was awarded from CM and now after completing my graduation from the ‘best fashion designing college of India’ I have my own Company with 550 employees. Got Youngest entrepreneur of the year award. Travelling Countries for my Fashion shows. Whenever any Radio interview/ my any Public Podcast people ask about my success. I never take this school name.\nI’m successful because of my dedication. My College principal.\nI would never suggest this school to any kid. Your inner creativity will die because of them.",
